-- TAIWAN GLASS IND May Sales Rise 2.86% (Table) : 1802 TT
-- B y   J a n e t   O n g
-- 2012-06-08T07:30:17Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-08/taiwan-glass-ind-may-sales-rise-2-86-table-1802-tt.html
TAIWAN GLASS IND said unconsolidated sales
in May rose 2.86% to NT$1,282,158,000 from NT$1,246,529,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  5/2012           5/2011
Sales           1,282,158        1,246,529   
YOY%              2.86%    -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           5,736,612        6,235,872   
YOY%              -8.01% 
=================================================================
 